# Installed / built inside the image — never copy from host
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.expo
**/.turbo
**/build
**/coverage
generated

# Secrets & local env (passed in at runtime, not baked into the image)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS, IDE, tooling, docs — not needed to build the API
.git
.gitignore
.idea
.vscode
.claude
.superpowers
.worktrees
docs

# OS cruft
**/.DS_Store
